headline: SRL Assigns Continuity Opinions to Lloyd’s Syndicates (Arch, Aspen, Axis, Hamilton, Lancashire, RenRe, Tokio Marine HCC, White Mountains, WR Berkley)
summary: LONDON, Oct. 23, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Syndicate Research Limited (SRL) has assigned Continuity Opinions (SCOs) to the following Lloyd’s syndicates, reflecting SRL's view of relative performance and continuity prospects for the syndicates over the insurance cycle. SRL commented that following these actions SCOs have now been assigned to 77% of Lloyd’s market capacity and scorecard indicators to 92% of market capacity; research is issued on all trading syndicates.
